==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[Internet]] [[Protocol]]'''

# {{internet}} One of the [[computer]] [[networking]] [[protocol|protocols]] that are anticedents or decendents of that specified by the [[IETF]] STD005, "INTERNET PROTOCOL"; all of which are characterized by providing [[routable]] network [[addressing]] and by being [[packet-switching|packet-switched]], [[unreliable]], and [[connectionless]].
# {{internet}} The most widely used of these protocols, [[IPv4]].

